message:
Parents often ask us “Who is being trafficked...where do the children come from?” This article explains dangers that put any child at risk. 

“It is like handing the red-light district to your child because it connects them to any predator that might decide to connect to that child for any reason.”| joplinglobe.com https://buff.ly/2X5spYc
